{"type": "article", "id": 22986, "title": "具有切割和搅拌的刀具", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-29T07:08:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 60, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071105491gX8F9oLs2JHAd5S.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这两片像叶子一样的工具集中了切割和搅拌沙拉等多个功能。其中一片下面的轮廓带有齿轮，两只手各拿一片时，以另一片的中间为板，可以实现简单的快速切割。切割好的蔬果放在碗中，这两个工具正好像大勺一样搅拌沙拉。产品目前还是一个概念。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110547fJjrqsGg6l9nyx5Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071105478bix0Il7Dk1Hejd9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110548Jqy73bGd5AK0OYnx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110548c4wsO7u0Bxo2jdlW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607110549LGlyOaDE5RX69UnZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.1952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}